Dual-Barcode-Demux
Copyright 2026 SCM

This workflow implements a demultiplexing workflow for 96-well combinatorial
row/column barcodes based on the published primer/barcode design described in
Nussbaum et al. The software implementation, packaging, and workflow interface
are authored by SCM.

This workflow is provided for research and educational use only. It is not
intended for clinical diagnosis, medical decision-making, patient care, or
regulated laboratory use without independent validation. See DISCLAIMER.md.

